{"id":1400,"category_slug":"english-conversations","category_name":"Conversations","position":96,"title":"96. Cafeteria menu","subtitle":"","level":"A2","parts":13,"url":"https://dailydictation.com/exercises/english-conversations/96-cafeteria-menu.1400/listen-and-type","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-cafeteria-menu-2024-07-21-17-33-24/0-conversation-cafeteria-menu.mp3","transcript":"Do you know what's on the menu at the cafeteria today?\nThey have grilled chicken,\na vegetarian pasta,\nand a soup of the day.\nDo you know if they have any gluten-free options?\nI'm trying to avoid gluten.\nLet me check...\nOkay, the grilled chicken is gluten-free.\nThey also have a quinoa salad that should be safe.\nGreat, thanks!\nDo you have any idea what the soup of the day is?\nI think it's mushroom soup,\nbut you might want to ask them to be sure.","youtube_video_id":"","details_cached_at":"2026-06-15T20:49:11","challenges":[{"position":1,"content":"Do you know what's on the menu at the cafeteria today?","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-cafeteria-menu-2024-07-21-17-33-24/1.mp3","time_start":0.36,"time_end":3.5},{"position":2,"content":"They have grilled chicken,","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-cafeteria-menu-2024-07-21-17-33-24/2.mp3","time_start":3.75,"time_end":5.21},{"position":3,"content":"a vegetarian pasta,","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-cafeteria-menu-2024-07-21-17-33-24/3.mp3","time_start":5.21,"time_end":6.81},{"position":4,"content":"and a soup of the day.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-cafeteria-menu-2024-07-21-17-33-24/4.mp3","time_start":6.81,"time_end":8.06},{"position":5,"content":"Do you know if they have any gluten-free options?","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-cafeteria-menu-2024-07-21-17-33-24/5.mp3","time_start":8.54,"time_end":10.91},{"position":6,"conten